OL,3,C'It's bonkers': British Gas tells
OL,4,Ccustomer he's #196,000 in credit
OL,6,FOne British Gas customer was told he
OL,7,Fwas nearly #200,000 in credit, as ITV
OL,8,FNews' Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FAn ITV News investigation has revealed
OL,12,Fhow British Gas told a customer he was
OL,13,Fmore than #196,000 in credit.
OL,15,FThe firm says it happened after
OL,16,Fsomeone in its team "inputted an
OL,17,Fincorrect meter reading" last August.
