OL,3,C'It's bonkers': British Gas tells
OL,4,Ccustomer he's #196,000 in credit
OL,6,FBritish Gas says the problem was
OL,7,Fcorrected in a day, but ridiculously
OL,8,Fhigh figures kept appearing on Rod
OL,9,FPeach's account and it's taken months
OL,10,Fto sort things out.
OL,12,FThe energy firm apologised and has
OL,13,Freduced his current bill by 50%.
OL,15,FHe joked: "Why are we paying British
OL,16,FGas bosses millions of pounds when
OL,17,Fthey owe me #196,000?"
