OL,3,C'It's bonkers': British Gas tells
OL,4,Ccustomer he's #196,000 in credit
OL,6,FBritish Gas says it's invested #50
OL,7,Fmillion more in consumer service since
OL,8,Fthe root causes of this problem,
OL,9,Fincluding 700 more call centre workers.
OL,11,FAlthough the company says customer
OL,12,Fservice is improving, the industry's
OL,13,Fregulator Ofgem insists that the whole
OL,14,Fsector needs to do better. It's clear
OL,15,Fthat British Gas does not have a
OL,16,Fmonopoly on mistakes like this.
OL,18,FIn Sheffield, we spoke to Allan
OL,19,FHartley who got different British Gas
OL,20,Fbills for the same period and received
OL,21,Fletters from their lawyers.
