OL,3,C'It's bonkers': British Gas tells
OL,4,Ccustomer he's #196,000 in credit
OL,6,FHe's in his 80s and was left afraid
OL,7,Fand confused.
OL,9,FHe told ITV News: "It's not fair, they
OL,10,Fshouldn't be treating people like
OL,11,Fthat, should they? I've been up in the
OL,12,Fmiddle of the night two or three times
OL,13,Fwith it on my mind."
OL,15,FBritish Gas says confusion was caused
OL,16,Fwhen several of Allan Hartley's bills
OL,17,Fwere reissued for the same period.
OL,19,FIt's apologised, saying things should
OL,20,Fhave been resolved sooner and
OL,21,Fexplained better.
