OL,3,C'It's bonkers': British Gas tells
OL,4,Ccustomer he's #196,000 in credit
OL,6,FThe company says his high bills were
OL,7,Fcaused by a backlog following
OL,8,Festimated readings.
OL,10,FThere was also a metering dispute
OL,11,Fafter it took over supplying him from
OL,12,Fa small energy firm that went bust.
OL,13,FAllan Hartley dismisses the company's
OL,14,Fclaims to have improved customer
OL,15,Fservice standards, as "ridiculous,
OL,16,Fdiabolical. It's not running better
OL,17,Fwhen they are treating people like
OL,18,Fthis is it?"
